{"Id":619688,"Title":"读南华外篇述以四言十五章 其十一 至乐","Dynasty":"明","Author":"郭之奇","Context":"乐与忧战，忧随乐遣。一死一生，忧乐乃见。人生所尊，富贵寿善。得之乃乐，乐之必恋。人生所恶，夭恶贫贱。得之乃忧，忧之必眩。以忧为生，生何足羡。去忧而死，死何足唁。百年长乐，已如流电。况其失之，何以终宴。人之所乐，随人而转。至乐无乐，终古莫倦。天清地宁，两无相衍。与时息消，使物周遍。吹气作人，如雨如霰。庄子盆歌，介叔柳变。髑髅髐然，岂易南面。海鸟临郊，愁窥牢膳。死骨欣欣，生禽悁悁。一气万形，古今一墠。生马生人，一炉千扇。出机入机，千轮一片。忧铄同门，死生同传。无乐之乐，乐谁我先。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"1975b6aa421149bee7e4e0d8bf33c8a1","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":7251112,"Sentence":"乐与忧战，忧随乐遣。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lè yú yōu zhàn ，yōu suǐ lè qiǎn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7251113,"Sentence":"一死一生，忧乐乃见。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yī si yī shēng ，yōu lè nǎi jiàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7251114,"Sentence":"人生所尊，富贵寿善。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rén shēng suǒ zūn ，fù guì shòu shàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7251115,"Sentence":"得之乃乐，乐之必恋。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dé zhī nǎi lè ，lè zhī bì liàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7251116,"Sentence":"人生所恶，夭恶贫贱。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rén shēng suǒ ě ，wāi ě pǐn jiàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7251117,"Sentence":"得之乃忧，忧之必眩。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dé zhī nǎi yōu ，yōu zhī bì xuàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7251118,"Sentence":"以忧为生，生何足羡。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yi yōu wéi shēng ，shēng hé zú xiàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7251119,"Sentence":"去忧而死，死何足唁。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qù yōu ér si ，si hé zú yàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7251120,"Sentence":"百年长乐，已如流电。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bǎi nián cháng lè ，yi rú lǐu diàn ","Tag"